data.description: MLS# 273008 This charming residential House in Central Pasco offers an ideal blend of comfort and convenience. With 5 Bedrooms and 3 Bathrooms , this spacious home is perfect for families or those who appreciate extra space. The generous living area spans 2145 sq ft, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment.Located just 2 blocks away from Pasco High School, this property is a great option for families with school going-children. Additionally , its strategic location endures quick access to various amenities. Within minutes in every direction, you'll find retail Shops, Supermarkets, Parks, a Hospital and a public Library, making daily life more convenient and enjoyable. Whether you're a first time homebuyer or looking for your forever home , this property is worth considering. The proximity to essential services and the ease of access to freeways make it a practical choice for those who value convenience in their daily lives. Don't miss out on this fantastic Opportunity! schedule a showing and explore the many possibilities this house has to offer.
